  "body": "Sometime database can be corrupted by external events, like unexpected power shutdown and PC restarts.\r\nIn such situations number of clients in Teku decreasing to zero.\r\n\r\nThe issue (and corresponding log files) is described here: \r\nhttps://github.com/ConsenSys/teku/issues/4377\r\n\r\nIn such situations Teku can detects this and \r\nideally drop the database and start it from scratch. \r\n\r\nInitialization using initial state this is a question of few minutes.",
