    "body": "Going to close this one. The aim is for the database to not get corrupted even with power interruptions etc and if there is an issue a) we want it to be noticed and reported so we can fix it and b) we don't want to delete data without manual intervention - the database issue may be able to be resolved by fixing permissions, freeing up disk space etc without necessarily having to delete the existing data.",
